The paper deals with instance search in video data, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of tracking to improve the performance of the system also involves machine learning techniques (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the combination of results from multiple instances, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and learning theory (cs.LG). Finally, the paper may also be relevant to cybersecurity (cs.CR) as it deals with tracking and identification of individuals in video data.
